These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, thriller, spy
1. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | thriller | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, car, subway
1. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
2. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Transport   | train | subway | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, architect, nurse
1. the architect is on the left of the freelancer##1
2. the freelancer is not to the right of the nurse##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Job   | architect | freelancer | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, board-games, reading
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |      3      |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, horror, documentary
1. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | horror | documentary |

