.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
2. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3   |
| Birthday   | june | december | january |

