.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
2. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |     2      |   3   |
| Sport   | rugby | lacrosse | skiing |

 